    {
      "id": "PopularPost2023",
      "post_content": "In my opinion, there are better cards out now - [Remand](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Remand), for example, requires the same amount of converted mana but requires one water and one colorless mana and allows you to draw a card. The drawback is that the card is returned to the opponent's hand and not the graveyard as it would be in this case. Counterspell is still a useful card for a blue deck and probably embodies the entire spirit of blue in Magic. I still use both this and [Remand](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Remand) in my red/blue Niv-Mizzet deck and I've found both to be useful in a pinch.",
      "posted_by": "Harpyja",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost2023\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">In my opinion, there are better cards out now - <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Remand\">Remand</a>, for example, requires the same amount of converted mana but requires one water and one colorless mana and allows you to draw a card. The drawback is that the card is returned to the opponent's hand and not the graveyard as it would be in this case. Counterspell is still a useful card for a blue deck and probably embodies the entire spirit of blue in Magic. I still use both this and <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Remand\">Remand</a> in my red/blue Niv-Mizzet deck and I've found both to be useful in a pinch.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: <a class=\"postedByLink\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\" id=\"PostedBy503\">Harpyja</a>\r\n                                (2/2/2009 11:56:38 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5