      "post_content": "Sometimes the oldest and simplest cards can be the best and [Counterspell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell ) is a primary example. Being able to stop anything as early as turn two can complete change the tempo of a game. The two blue mana cost may appear pesky to some, but as long as your playing mono-blue or running duel lands, then there should't be any real objection to this card. Oh, and the art work for this version of [Counterspell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell) is epic.",
      "posted_by": "SavageBrain89",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"RecentPost7434\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_recentPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Sometimes the oldest and simplest cards can be the best and <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell \">Counterspell </a>is a primary example.  Being able to stop anything as early as turn two can complete change the tempo of a game.  The two blue mana cost may appear pesky to some, but as long as your playing mono-blue or running duel lands, then there should't be any real objection to this card.  Oh, and the art work for this version of <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell\">Counterspell</a> is epic.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_recentPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_recentPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: <a class=\"postedByLink\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\" id=\"PostedBy636\">SavageBrain89</a>\r\n                                (5/23/2009 9:30:18 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_recentPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.gif\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/R